# Run scripts/prepare_vectors.py to generate vocab.json and vectors.bin here.
# See README for instructions.
#
# Expected layout:
#   data/glove/vocab.json
#   data/glove/vectors.bin
#   data/googlenews/vocab.json   (optional — needed for Google News toggle)
#   data/googlenews/vectors.bin
#   data/twitter/vocab.json      (optional — needed for GloVe Twitter toggle)
#   data/twitter/vectors.bin
